CatDescriptText: In back row: Reverend Charles Foggie, fourth from left and Harrington is fifth from left. In front row: Webster, second from left; Griffin, fourth from left, and Reverend Pettus, sixth from left.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of fourteen men, including Reverend Charles Foggie and Mr. Harrington in back, with Mr. Webster, Fred Griffin, and Rev. Pettus, in front row, inside Wesley Center AME Zion Church, possibly for Ministers conference
